{"type":"article_comment","id":243284,"parentType":"article","parentId":13688,"uid":25631,"contents":"<blockquote>这篇文章似乎被鹅组粉红们发现了。https://www.douban.com/group/topic...</blockquote><br>\n这篇文章已经被删掉了，存档：<br>\nWayback Machine<br>\n可以看到被迫害的用户已经改名了。用户 ID 是 <u>62470277</u>。<br>\n<br>\n全文备份如下：<br>\n<blockquote><b>标题：</b>很郑重的提醒一下七组鹅们，最近小心自己的id被用来恶意注册<br>\n我今天刚刚被组鹅告知我的id 被恨国d拿来注册“墙外版知乎”品葱<br>\n顺便给大家科普一下 这个网站是个什么玩意儿<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666573.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666573.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666573.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666574.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666574.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244666574.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n有人发帖并制作教程教唆其他人用七组或者豆瓣其他小组成员的id和个人隐私来伪装一个账号<br>\n<br>\n他们可能会利用大家的豆瓣id和照片等的信息 披上你的身份在网络论坛上面发布反动信息 造谣带节奏 比如骂lder或者恶搞gov<br>\n希望可以让更多组鹅知道 在这里提醒广大兄弟姐妹<br>\n注意不要暴露隐私 最好把豆瓣照片等涉及自身信息的相关内容都转为私密<br>\n也谢谢发私信告诉我的姐妹 🙏<br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665935.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665935.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665935.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n这些图都是他们发出去的教程 教别人如何注册 这个bi用的是我的id 现在我都打上码了<br>\n<center><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665941.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665941.jpg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20200212143215im_/https://img3.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p244665941.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></center><br>\n有气又担心又好笑 不懂这群节奏大师图什么？看我们这么爱国不反动 他们根本带不起来 一定很气吧</blockquote><br>\n<br>\n不过品葱的维基百科写得真的不怎么样。","date":"2020-02-13","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}